description: Get a bulk supply of register information to save time spent manually ordering individual copies.

details.body:
If you need title information for more than 20 properties, use our Volume Register Service.

For each title number supplied, you receive the register entry information as a PDF or CSV file. Additional information from the register is also available on request.

Cost

Prices start from £7.50 per title number (excluding VAT).

More information

To find out more about this service, please contact:

Data Services Team

HM Land Registry
Rosebrae Court
Woodside Ferry Approach
Birkenhead
Merseyside
CH41 6DU

Email data.services@mail.landregistry.gov.uk

Contact form https://customerhelp.l...

Telephone 0300 006 0478
